1. *Ruski* medvedi su veoma krupni. (Russian bears are very large.)
2. Mnogi ljudi u Srbiji uče *ruski* jezik. (Many people in Serbia are learning the Russian language.)
3. Ona je kupila *ruske* knjige u knjižari. (She bought Russian books at the bookstore.)
4. *Ruska* salata se pravi od krompira i povrća. (Russian salad is made from potatoes and vegetables.)
5. *Ruski* tenkovi su osvojili grad. (Russian tanks captured the city.)
6. *Ruske* železnice su jako razvijene. (Russian railways are highly developed.)
7. Ovaj restoran služi *rusku* hranu. (This restaurant serves Russian food.)
8. Čuo sam da su *ruski* turisti veoma brojni ove godine. (I heard that Russian tourists are very numerous this year.)
9. On je pročitao *rusku* knjigu za samo jedan dan. (He read a Russian book in just one day.)
10. *Ruskim* diplomama se u Srbiji priznaju kao visoko obrazovanje. (Russian diplomas are recognized as higher education in Serbia.)